### 1. Obtener todas las acciones
GET http://localhost:5168/api/stock
Accept: application/json

### 2. Crear una acción de Apple (AAPL)
POST http://localhost:5168/api/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "companyName": "Apple Inc.",
  "purchasePrice": 150.50,
  "quantity": 10
}

### 3. Crear una acción de Microsoft (MSFT)
POST http://localhost:5168/api/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "MSFT",
  "companyName": "Microsoft Corp.",
  "purchasePrice": 310.00,
  "quantity": 5
}

### 4. Actualizar Microsoft (Cambiar precio y cantidad)
PUT http://localhost:5168/api/stock/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "MSFT",
  "companyName": "Microsoft Corporation Updated",
  "purchasePrice": 350.00,
  "quantity": 50
}

### 5. Eliminar Apple (ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:5168/api/stock/1

### 6. Intentar crear una acción inválida (Debería fallar)
POST http://localhost:5168/api/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "ESTE_SIMBOLO_ES_MUY_LARGO_PARA_SER_REAL",
  "companyName": "",
  "purchasePrice": -50.00,
  "quantity": 0
}

### 7. Crear comentario para el Stock 2 (Microsoft)
POST http://localhost:5168/api/comment/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Gran inversión",
  "content": "Creo que Microsoft va a subir mucho este año."
}

### 8. Ver todos los comentarios
GET http://localhost:5168/api/comment